{"id":595068,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/09/【网络民议】害死她的还有对整个国家的失望/","date":"2018-09-07T15:45:05Z","modified":"2018-09-07T15:45:05Z","title":"【网络民议】害死她的还有对整个国家的失望","content":"<p>编者按：9月7日一位华安基金受害者的遗书、自杀照片以及生前维权视频在网络流传，也引起网民们对华安基金的愤怒声讨，同时网民认为：“女孩的遗书，字字戳心，看得流泪！害死她的不仅仅是因为被骗的几十万，还有维权过程中收到的打击，政府经侦的不作为，骗子华安嚣张的态度，警察暴力执法的心寒，是对整个社会整个国家的失望！”</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595069\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/201809072314china2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/201809072314china2.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/201809072314china2-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595075\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/6267f300gy1fv0t6xrkzij20mi0u0q9e.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/6267f300gy1fv0t6xrkzij20mi0u0q9e.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/6267f300gy1fv0t6xrkzij20mi0u0q9e-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595076\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Image-from-iOS-2-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"522\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Image-from-iOS-2-4.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Image-from-iOS-2-4-287x300.jpg 287w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Image-from-iOS-2-4-768x802.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/Image-from-iOS-2-4-980x1024.jpg 980w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595077\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/007eGGq0ly1fukg7ngtpaj30c8081q3d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"328\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/20